Border Lighting - Edge Lighting: Privacy Policy
Last Updated:
January 29, 2025
Introduction
The Border Lighting - Edge Lighting app for iOS respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines the data we collect, how we use it, and how we ensure its security. By using our app, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
Data We Do NOT Collect:
Analytical Data:
We do not collect any form of analytical data, including anonymous analytics or crash logs.
Screenshots and Data:
We do not access or read your screenshots or the data within them. Text recognition, if used, is powered by Apple's Vision Kit and all processing occurs on-device. No data is sent to external servers.
User Activity:
We do not track or monitor your activity within the app beyond what is necessary to provide its functionality.
Permissions We Request:
1. Accessibility Permission
Purpose:
Required to take screenshots for use within the app.
Assurance:
We do not read, store, or transmit any data contained in your screenshots.
2. Device Information
Purpose:
When you activate a license key, we collect:
Device Name (e.g., “iPhone 14 Pro Max”):
Used for identifying your device in the License Manager.
Device ID (hardware identifier):
Used to prevent misuse of the license key across unauthorized devices.
Data We Collect:
1. License Activation Data
Data Collected:
Device Name
Device ID (hardware identifier)
Usage:
Exclusively for license management to ensure authorized usage.
Sharing:
We do not share this information with any third-party services.
2. Subscription Information:
If you subscribe to one of our plans, we may collect non-identifiable purchase information (e.g., subscription status) directly from Apple to manage your access to premium features.
Subscription Information:
The Border Lighting - Edge Lighting app offers the following subscription options:
Edge Lighting Monthly Subscription
Price:
$1.99 per month
Terms:
Auto-renews monthly.
Features Included:
Access to premium edge lighting effects.
Customizable lighting styles.
Regular feature updates and improvements.
Edge Lighting Yearly Subscription
Price:
$9.99 per year
Terms:
Auto-renews annually.
Features Included:
All features from the monthly subscription.
Enjoy a discounted rate compared to the monthly plan.
Includes a
7-day free trial
.
Important Subscription Terms:
Free Trial for Annual Plan:
The yearly subscription includes a 7-day free trial period. During this period, you will have access to all premium features.
If you do not cancel before the trial ends, your subscription will automatically renew, and your account will be charged $9.99 for the year.
Auto-Renewal:
By subscribing, you agree to the auto-renewal terms. At the end of each billing period, your subscription will automatically renew and charge your account unless canceled at least 24 hours before the renewal date.
Managing Subscriptions:
You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time through your device's
Settings > Subscriptions
. Canceling a subscription will stop the auto-renewal but does not provide refunds for the current billing period.
Cookies and Tracking Technologies:
We do not use cookies or any other tracking technologies in this app. All functionality is provided without requiring tracking or analytics.
Third-Party Services:
We do not share, sell, or rent your personal data to third-party services. The only instance we may share your data is if required by law or for compliance with legal obligations.
Data Retention:
We retain the data we collect only for as long as necessary to provide the services you request. For license activation data, this information is securely stored and deleted if no longer required for service functionality. We take commercially reasonable measures to protect your information from loss, theft, or unauthorized access.
Children’s Privacy:
Our app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal information from children. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected data from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information promptly.
External Links:
Our app may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before engaging with them.
EU/EEA Users (GDPR Compliance):
If you are located in the European Union (EU) or European Economic Area (EEA), you have the following rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR):
Access:
You have the right to request access to the personal data we store about you.
Correction:
You can request corrections to any inaccurate or incomplete data.
Erasure:
You can request that we delete your personal data, subject to certain conditions.
Objection:
You can object to the processing of your data.
To exercise your GDPR rights, please contact us at
thuyenpham.dev@gmail.com
.
Your Rights:
You can refuse our request for your personal information; however, this may limit your ability to access some features of the app.
You can manage your subscription and data preferences through your device settings.
Apple’s Standard EULA:
We use Apple's standard End-User License Agreement (EULA) for the app. You can view the details here:
Apple Standard EULA
.
Changes to This Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last Updated" date. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your data.
Contact Us:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us:
Email:
thuyenpham.dev@gmail.com
Website:
https://futfc.vercel.app/
